    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 2.5",
    "body" : "<p><code>ImmutableList</code> is similar to <code>Collections.unmodifiableList( new ArrayList( list ) )</code> . Note that the newly created <code>ArrayList</code> is <strong>not</strong> assigned to a field or variable.</p>\n"
